  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-515dc327-8692-413a-bcfc-49292f110a0e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-161285e2-65c7-4c6c-9175-d3a430570aca\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-95a05ef6-d8e8-4245-8e8f-b850ecf83cda\">몇 일 전, 폭염 주의 문자가 왔습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-39d14a53-36b5-4ad3-a99b-117f7ac78f4b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-879eebf4-0c9c-419e-bccc-6584bfbcf4a3\">본격적인 더위가 시작되네요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8cd6e687-9c07-4194-a7cc-0f9f1955248f\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-c178e1fd-1ea4-4a1f-a80d-b0179350eb30\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-23d2318e-6c28-437e-bf8c-c8341787bc58\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-205b51a8-69f9-43fb-9865-b94a0439c23a\">더운 여름은 아무래도 노출이 많은 옷을 입게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5bbf1190-a319-4b2b-b370-d372f6d065ed\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-647e326a-7171-4d39-8bdd-6ae99b8e376d\">멋을 위해서 뿐 아니라, 더위를 이겨내기 위해 불가피한 선택이죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-59e10231-29c9-487d-bb55-c7855f533405\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-c1e6f394-11db-499e-8280-076380312983\">그러나보니, 눈에 보이는 살들이 더욱 신경 쓰입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0ddd71f8-0e37-4a7e-bdcd-ae425631c4a4\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-a96dae05-671d-40ac-8f8b-ff45ef970ae3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-11cb359d-a2c8-4324-a199-bcda23acc4d3\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-fe3b2dbc-f2de-4d7d-9136-45f642ead458\">그래서 결심합니다. 다이어트해야지~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-da39ab6a-ce33-49aa-a702-93c3f2027464\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-0655ae06-2526-4388-9510-f8b83ce486f8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f5f2e906-abaa-4756-bf44-3e7f44a78dfa\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:292px;\">\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f5f2e906-abaa-4756-bf44-3e7f44a78d