-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-12bdff39-50ff-4635-8324-f702199c5e99\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-0b52d5d4-027d-4f54-be80-a6b5f7814712\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e512d612-51c9-4e77-bb0e-6ad379ac964e\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-cb74a2d0-8411-4ed2-9917-bb7eb24a8c31\">반면, 삼겹살 100g 330kcal, 사과1개 140kcal, 짜장면 1인분 약800kcal 정도 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fc4c47df-5d50-4cd1-b156-4b7749430872\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:480px;\">\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-fc4c47df-5d50-4cd1-b156-4b7749430872\", \"src\" : \"http://image.chosun.com/sitedata/image/201309/12/2013091201301_0.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"http://image.chosun.com/sitedata/image/201309/12/2013091201301_0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-385f59ce-82d2-4d7a-9d0a-89dbbb08e78d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3f195260-637c-4045-b6d1-60238279dfe9\">출처 - 조선비즈</span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5fa2de1e-025c-4d6f-baae-d8099955e313\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e2d5ec28-5c84-4e8e-87dd-acb7c9c0da06\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-d2028fc7-5997-4455-9195-5c86c5e02705\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4f063d0c-d9bc-4c47-9c09-badc544dda10\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:250px;\">\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4f063d0c-d9bc-4c47-9c09-badc544dda10\", \"src\" : \"http://pds.joins.com/news/component/htmlphoto_mmdata/201111/23/htm_201111230555730103011.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"http://pds.joins.com/news/component/htmlphoto_mmdata/201111/23/htm_201111230555730103011.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-71d8ea86-f185-4083-82d0-1bd54de4e526\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a48e43ba-3068-4196-be4a-8381a2ba5936\">출처 - 중앙일보</span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d71f337b-ffe6-471f-b45f-26f4652a22a3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eac5e4bb-8f1f-462b-8e79-8c48deb66af9\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-bab0d94e-a86f-45f3-88fe-a270ef385a27\"> 따라서 식사나 간식을 조금 덜 먹으면 1시간 이상 운동한 효과를 낼 수 있습니다(운동의 다른 영향을 제외하고 단순 칼로리 소비의 관점만 봤을 때 입니다). </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ca9bc6b2-065a-499e-a5bf-6e99968739ea\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-6596c8d5-925d-4f78-b4d2-81ad1d6aee5d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cfe76bb3-7cd0-49b7-ae6d-059fd406789c\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-b5a8701c-c287-4973-a5e2-251577ddc406\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-45484112-b9f3-4709-8f42-4c8163099ef5\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-a9fdd6eb-5756-47b9-9c59-46001fa24a8e\">섭취 열량의 제한은 적정량의 30% 정도를 생각하면 되겠습니다. 30% 정도의 칼로리 섭취 제한은 우리 몸에 많은 이득을 준다고 연구되고 있습니다(특히 수명의 연장효과가 있어 &#x27;장수&#x27;할 수 있게 한다는 연구들이 있습니다). </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-15328388-a21d-4475-b260-43bd314ffb66\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-87418b04-4682-4a25-9de3-a88da65129fb\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a768697-7b2f-47ef-8195-776f6a1ea29b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-607385f0-feac-4a3c-8471-4a00eb0a1a23\">한국영양학회 자료에 따르면 나이별 1일 필요 칼로리는 아래와 같습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1516ed07-731a-4991-9537-77458756a5ca\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:474px;\">\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-1516ed07-731a-4991-9537-77458756a5ca\", \"src\" : \"http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/MjAxODAyMjdfMTkx/MDAxNTE5NzAxMjM2NTQy.EA9vejWkprDT52NDO34JMaZtj-MmSFumDR6n2xmzBmAg.EIXWypi2ilP_XgqX9LLyAZmZgMnvopsfvDesCXApncUg.GIF.fitness_day/11.gif?type=w800\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAxODAyMjdfMTkx/MDAxNTE5NzAxMjM2NTQy.EA9vejWkprDT52NDO34JMaZtj-MmSFumDR6n2xmzBmAg.EIXWypi2ilP_XgqX9LLyAZmZgMnvopsfvDesCXApncUg.GIF.fitness_day/11.gif?type=w800\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ef101475-6ac2-4ec9-a0f8-e6d6ce82100e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-24b8ede1-9e11-4213-86bb-b2310b74aa66\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-f646da68-1950-4f6e-8cbe-d1761e7c18b2\">30대 여성 기준으로 보면 하루 필요 칼로리는 2000kcal 이고, 여기서 30%를 줄이면 1400kcal 정도가 되겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-abc78298-95e0-4cfa-9f9a-b25c8639be62\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-483f52ad-f6c9-4910-ad01-2759cb0827ea\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8acd486c-368f-4b57-868e-4aa840adbdf8\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-0f2ff384-7317-4136-bbe4-4e2fd9948dd2\">빠른 체중감량을 위해서는 이보다 더 적게 먹어야 합니다. 하루 섭취량을 800kcal 미만으로 제한하는 것을 초저열량식이라고 하는데, 건강에 해롭기 때문에 권장하지 않습니다. 30대 여성 기초대사량인 1170kcal에 맞춰 식사를 하면 적당할 듯 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-06433359-55f6-49c6-a07a-bd424c87080c\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-8a791de9-3e46-4b87-9efb-4a77ac7aa8a8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-97efe403-0e57-4a82-affe-a19400715d66\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-fcb95ea9-f532-4b93-876f-487f099b7ee9\">다이어트가 끝난 후에는 하루 1400kcal 섭취를 목표로 삼고 식습관을 개선하면 되겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8aeb1a6e-b317-4db5-9941-d496df381b4f\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ba10e60c-366d-4edf-8eb2-bde781241824\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cf012a41-6475-4945-8126-1f4c88f92433\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module se-module-image __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\" \" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-cf012a41-6475-4945-8126-1f4c88f92433\", \"src\" : \"https://pds.joins.com/news/component/htmlphoto_mmdata/200904/htm_2009040916265770007400-001.JPG\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://pds.joins.com/news/component/htmlphoto_mmdata/200904/htm_2009040916265770007400-001.JPG\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                </a>                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3238348f-3173-4fd2-a487-bf2bdc3311db\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e567eb91-acab-4fb9-9206-9574c7ceeb84\">출처 - 조인스닷컴</span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1de08a37-34f8-48e4-91f8-4926a8b78e7a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7e72c664-07d0-4998-aaa9-67d0770f185b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-f55d4c7a-1c8a-4a2d-b35e-81056e05d0f9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a1e6a70-2f01-43e9-a920-b0ab5cc32278\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-c6a8eb8e-7a21-4411-98cf-ac22cd1c340c\">섭취하는 영양의 구성도 조절하면 좋습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-549c61f7-49f1-4429-a022-fcb5c8b8477d\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-32929308-d6c2-4cc2-bced-9e00dc2aab79\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7bbb85fd-23ed-4a82-a174-c276d588172e\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3771b784-28a0-40b5-b7fb-720eb5fd6513\">탄수화물(밥, 면, 빵, 설탕 등)의 섭취는 줄이세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8af34ad9-6731-4814-9b38-76b3f7e7e266\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-eb59ed62-f231-4cf1-ad13-970fa633b501\">대신 단백질은 매일 적당량을 드세요. (매일 80-90g 정도의 살코기(닭 가슴살 등)를 먹거나 삶은 계란 흰자 4~5개를 드시면 됩니다. 생선도 좋습니다.)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-302d3c55-0d0c-47bd-acf2-b6b577b1a602\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3a589ab6-c966-4d53-9171-a6b05afc170d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-34e77a01-4d16-45f1-a333-af35759a333e\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-b963da0e-4b20-4401-8f54-cb6cb23c8459\">매일 먹는 음식을 마시는 것, 먹는 것 가릴 것 없이 입에 들어간 것은 모두 종류와 양을 기록하세요. 먹는 것을 기록하는 사람들이 다이어트에 성공하는 확률이 높다는 연구가 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c7b65874-fa24-453f-82d0-b73f6a9241cb\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-884ff677-843d-4a99-8fce-5db608ad5ac4\">마찬가지로,  운동 및 활동한 것도 기록하도록 하세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e74163d6-3c15-4c4a-9140-2f75689360d6\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-55b851a9-ed69-446e-b708-c8f99c7ead98\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f540f428-9cd5-4c11-92b1-8d6f10197a20\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-e1a8b276-7cc6-420e-88d2-4140490727a2\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-68a91dce-59de-4df8-a665-343d68cba069\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-38f7ba82-79c6-41dd-990b-f289127d9b51\">그리고, 결심했으면 목표를 달성할 때까지 포기하지 말고 계속 노력하세요. 꼭!!!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87f69155-d0da-4fbf-9d21-a7b3de2e2e3f\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-e7e8ea49-bed7-46e9-b86f-6db2ed97810b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a411c95a-839f-4813-83c0-4704efa39fff\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5fc8e180-02de-4897-81f6-c04c699bace5\">혼자서 하기 힘들 것 같나요? </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b357868d-2e62-4bd4-a27c-2e64bdea216b\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-121d628e-9e82-469d-9648-870401c6a338\">걱정마세요! </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b41796d6-49e3-4768-a57e-b8f2c405e1b3\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-1914d60e-2bdc-4be8-acd0-d80d4d3ef344\">이수한의원이 다이어트한약과 지방분해침치료, 주기적 상담으로 성공적인 다이어트를 도와드립니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f8b91950-3c55-4e66-8df1-cb0e109d8874\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-96c43c07-06c9-4261-9cbf-bbfb6d392905\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d4013821-599e-4a40-95f7-81c7995cb279\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-modu